'''莉莎·畢法露'''（{{lang-en|Lisa Bufano}}，{{bd|1972年|10月20日|2013年|10月3日|catIdx=Bufano}}）<ref name="vmpandco1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.vmpandco.com/obituaries/Lisa-Bufano/#!/Obituary|title=Ms. Lisa Bufano Obituary: Visitation & Funeral Information|accessdate=2013-11-12|author=Family of Lisa Bufano|publisher=Vmpandco.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029201826/http://www.vmpandco.com/obituaries/Lisa-Bufano/#!/Obituary|archivedate=2013-10-29}}</ref>，是一個殘疾美國跨學科的表演藝術家，其作品加入娃娃製作，面料做工，動畫和舞蹈元素。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=7728628|title=Artist Takes Inspiration from Amputation|accessdate=2015-03-29|date=|work=Npr.org|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402130742/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=7728628|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 早年生活 ==
莉莎·畢法露出生于[[路易斯|路易斯]]家庭，2003年她毕业于[[布里奇波特|布里奇波特康涅狄格]][[塔夫茨大學|塔夫茨大學]]<ref name="vmpandco1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.vmpandco.com/obituaries/Lisa-Bufano/#!/Obituary|title=Ms. Lisa Bufano Obituary: Visitation & Funeral Information|accessdate=2013-11-12|author=Family of Lisa Bufano|publisher=Vmpandco.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029201826/http://www.vmpandco.com/obituaries/Lisa-Bufano/#!/Obituary|archivedate=2013-10-29}}</ref>，後來在[[波士頓美術館學校|波士頓美術館學校]]就读。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.smfa.edu/lisa-bufano |title=Lisa Bufano |accessdate=2016-07-19 |archive-date=2013-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130224094934/http://www.smfa.edu/lisa-bufano |dead-url=no }}</ref>作为一个孩子，她是一个有競爭力的體操運動員<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.body-pixel.com/2008/05/24/lisa-bufano-%E2%80%93-the-spiderwoman|title=Lisa Bufano – the Spiderwoman|accessdate=2013-11-12|publisher=Body Pixel|archive-date=2013-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102162928/http://www.body-pixel.com/2008/05/24/lisa-bufano-%e2%80%93-the-spiderwoman/|dead-url=no}}</ref>同时也是{{link-en|Go-go 舞者|Go-go_dancer}}。21岁时，因为一个威胁生命的[[葡萄球菌属|葡萄球菌]][[病原细菌|細菌感染]]，她下肢和拇指需要截肢。

==死亡==
2013年10月3日，莉莎·畢法露在[[舊金山|舊金山]]自殺，且沒有[[遺書|遺書]]被發現。兩個月後，她的哥哥对莉莎·畢法露的死因感到莫名其妙。
{{cquote|我被莉莎·畢法露生活的猜測圍繞。facebook上，朋友，家人和她的粉丝全部都想知道。他们希望有一个合理的原因。这样他们感觉会好些。他們希望莉莎·畢法露回來。

但是這一切有很大的困難。莉莎·畢法露並不像其他人突出自己的想法。我們永遠不會明白為什麼她会自杀。它永遠不會是有合理的原因的。

我相信她的生命，而她的人生是許多人的生命。我不相信這是短的生命。她的任務已经完成了，她一定已經明白和面臨她離開了這個世界。她獨自一人與她的狗在半夜的家里。<ref name="autogenerated1"/>}}

{{quote|<blockquote>''I’m surrounded by speculation about why Lisa took her own life. Facebook, friends, family members, and her fans would all like to know. They want it to make sense to them. They want to feel okay. Ultimately they want her back.''

''But I am having great difficulty with all of this. Lisa didn’t like other people projecting their idea of who she was on her. We’ll never understand why. It will never make sense.''

''I believe she lived her entire life and that her life was many lives. I don’t believe it was cut-off short. Her mission was completed and she must have understood that fact when she departed from this world. She was alone with her dog in her home in the middle of the night.''<ref name="autogenerated1"/></blockquote>
}}

